The paper also mentions the use of spatiotemporal representations and activities, which suggests that the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category may also be relevant. The paper also discusses the robots' ability to improve their own performance over time, which suggests that the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category may be relevant. Finally, the paper discusses the robots' ability to operate autonomously in real environments, which suggests that the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category may also be relevant.
